com.pedroalmir.athena.core.type.container
Class Vector.Builder

java.lang.Object
  com.pedroalmir.athena.core.type.container.Vector.Builder
Enclosing class:
Vector
public static class Vector.Builder
extends java.lang.Object

A builder for creating Vector instances. It is especially useful for creating constant instances that do not change:

Example: 

public static final Vector IDENTITY
       = Vector.newBuilder()
          .add(1.0)
          .add(0.0)
          .build()

Builder instances can be reused - it is safe to call build() multiple times to build multiple Vectors in series. Each new vector contains the one created before it.
